<gpx xmlns="http://www.topografix.com/GPX/1/1" xmlns:gpxx="http://www.garmin.com/xmlschemas/GpxExtensions/v3" creator="CALTOPO" version="1.1"><metadata><name><![CDATA[4 Peaks Loop]]></name></metadata><trk><name>4 Peaks Loop</name><desc>Popularity: 2/5
Difficulty: 5/5
Dates: 6/1 - 11/1

Think Santa Fe Baldy is too easy? Think 3 peaks isn't enough? Well then do it all. Hit the 4 major peaks near Santa Fe: Deception, Lake, Penitente, and Baldy; plus get Lake Katherine as a bonus. Oof that's a lot of vert, but the incredible views, beautiful trails for running, and exhausted bliss at the end is worth it.</desc><trkseg><trkpt lat="35.79549521375863" lon="-105.80464597381592"><ele>3131.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79555254997097" lon="-105.80466672438035"><ele>3131.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79555254997097" lon="-105.80466672438035"><ele>3131.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79555" lon="-105.80468000000002"><ele>3131.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79563" lon="-105.80484000000001"><ele>3131.757373727858</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79576" lon="-105.80484000000001"><ele>3132.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.7958" lon="-105.80478"><ele>3132.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79603" lon="-105.80464999999998"><ele>3132.425404445268</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79603" lon="-105.80464999999998"><ele>3132.425404445268</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79608" lon="-105.80464"><ele>3132.654862740286</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79608" lon="-105.80464"><ele>3132.654862740286</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79616" lon="-105.80462999999997"><ele>3134.2093720454723</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79616" lon="-105.80462999999997"><ele>3134.2093720454723</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79616" lon="-105.80462999999997"><ele>3134.2093720454723</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.7962" lon="-105.80457999999999"><ele>3135.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79644" lon="-105.80414000000002"><ele>3138.2973022162914</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79662" lon="-105.80405000000002"><ele>3142.391782510197</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79672" lon="-105.80394999999999"><ele>3143.3852890841663</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79689" lon="-105.80385999999999"><ele>3147.153023056686</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79693" lon="-105.80380000000002"><ele>3147.4513164442033</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.79709" lon="-105.80374"><ele>3151.0</ele></